Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:01.15,Main,Renne,0,0,0,,{Oh! Tou—}Ah, Kak Touya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:02.77,Main,Renne,0,0,0,,{Sir Touya!}Ah, Tuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.77,0:04:05.25,Main,Cecil,0,0,0,,{Welcome back, Sir Touya.}Selamat datang, Tuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:07.80,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{I'm home, Renne, Cecil-san.}Aku pulang, Renne, Cecil-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:09.83,Main,Renne,0,0,0,,{Did you defeat the Mythril Golems?}Sudah kalahkan Golem Mithril?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:10.56,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:12.61,Main,Renne,0,0,0,,{Then you earned the Red rank?}Berarti sudah peringkat Merah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:16.18,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{I did. Yumina's now Blue, \Nand the rest of us are Red.}Iya. Yumina Biru, kami Merah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:21.34,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Now we're all considered \Nfirst-rate adventurers.}Dengan begini, kami sudah \Njadi petualang kelas atas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:24.56,Main,Cecil,0,0,0,,{Sir Touya, I've prepared the bath for you.}Tuan, air untuk mandi sudah siap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.56,0:04:26.97,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Thank you. Then everyone else can go first.}Makasih. Kalau 'gitu, \Nsana yang lain duluan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:27.99,Main,Renne,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Lo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:30.65,Main,Renne,0,0,0,,{Where's Miss Cesca?}Kak Cesca mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:32.55,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Oh...}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:38.24,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{I forgot her...}Kelupaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.02,0:04:44.66,Main,Cesca,0,0,0,,{It does not bother me at all.}Aku tidak terlalu peduli, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.66,0:04:46.62,Main,Cesca,0,0,0,,{I do not mind one bit}Termasuk kalau Master meninggalkanku ...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:49.87,Main,Cesca,0,0,0,,{that you left me behind and \Nquickly returned home, Master.}... dan langsung pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:52.35,Main,Cesca,0,0,0,,{No, not one bit.}Tidak, sangat tidak keberatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:05:00.68,Main,Cesca,0,0,0,,{Thanks to this, I have learned my new \Nmaster has a fetish for abandonment play.}Berkat ini, aku bisa tahu bahwa Master \Npunya fetish baru, meninggalkan orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:04.06,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{I don't have even an ounce \Nof that fetish, okay?!}Aku sama sekali \Ntidak punya fetish begituan, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:10.27,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{I do feel bad about it!}Aku salah, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:12.87,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{I just used Gate to return home out of habit.}Kelepasan pakai Gate ....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:15.90,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{I think that's enough.}Sudah cukup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:18.55,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{He truly seems to regret it,}Toh sepertinya \Nsudah sadar kesalahannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.55,0:05:21.86,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{and if you're too persistent, \Nhe really will abandon you.}Kalau terlalu bersikeras, \Nbakal benaran ditinggalkan, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.37,0:05:25.12,Main,Cesca,0,0,0,,{That would be unpleasant.}Yah, repot, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:31.13,Main,Cesca,0,0,0,,{Then I'll forgive you if you buy me \Nnaughty underwear that's to your liking.}Baiklah, kalau Master mau memberiku \Ncelana dalam seksi favorit, maka akan kumaafkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.13,0:05:32.46,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{That's a huge hurdle!}Syaratnya mahal amat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.46,0:05:34.24,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Even normal ones would be impossible!}Celana dalam biasa juga tidak boleh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.24,0:05:35.47,Main,Cesca,0,0,0,,{I jest.}Bercanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:42.62,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Jeez...}Ya ampun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.62,0:05:45.79,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{Those thought circuits of \Nhers really are incredible.}Tapi daya berpikirnya hebat, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.79,0:05:47.71,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{How is that perverted mind incredible?}Mananya yang hebat \Ndari pemikiran mesum itu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.71,0:05:52.04,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{It's her ability to pout, and the \Nflexibility needed to tell jokes.}Maksudku sikap ngambeknya dan \Nfleksibilitasnya membuat lelucon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.04,0:05:54.02,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{She's like a real person.}Seperti orang sungguhan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:57.51,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{I wonder if it's even possible to \Nreach that point with Program.}Entah bisa sejauh apa pakai Program.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.37,0:06:04.41,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{So, what did you want today?}Jadi, hari ini ada urusan apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:08.31,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{To talk about the teleportation circles \Nto the remaining Babylons.}Mengenai susunan teleportasi \NBabylon yang tersisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.31,0:06:11.62,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{At the moment, we don't have \Nany definite information.}Hingga kini, aku \Nbelum dapat informasi pasti.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:13.46,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Huh? You plan to search for them?}Eh? Mau kamu cari?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:15.44,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{Huh? You }{\i1}{don't}{\i0}{ plan to search for them?}Eh? Enggak kamu cari?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:19.65,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{To be honest, I can't think \Nof a reason to look for them.}Jujur, aku tidak nemu \Nalasan untuk mencarinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:20.88,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{Why not?!}Kenapa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:24.98,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{Don't you want to know more about \Nancient knowledge or lost technology?}Tidak ingin tahu lebih dalam mengenai Teknologi \Ndan Pengetahuan Kuno yang telah hilang?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:26.81,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{I don't.}Tidak niat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.81,0:06:31.64,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Professor Babylon even said that this era \Ndoesn't need power that's too strong.}Kata Profesor Babylon juga tidak \Nperlu kekuatan besar untuk era ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.64,0:06:33.85,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{You're a young man with no dreams!}Dasar pemuda tidak punya mimpi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:38.44,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Well, I'll think about it once you have \Ninformation on a teleportation circle.}Yah, ayo pikirkan setelah ada \Nlaporan tentang teleportasinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.44,0:06:41.07,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{If you're sure we can find one, \NI'll help you with it.}Akan kubantu kalau \Nsudah nemu yang pasti.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.07,0:06:42.48,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{That's a promise.}Janji, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.48,0:06:46.14,Main,Leen,0,0,0,,{If you break it, you'll be buying naughty \Nunderwear for me, too, you hear?}Kalau ingkar, belikan \Nkancut seksi buatku juga, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:48.04,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Please spare me that!}Lupakan saja!
