Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.07,0:07:27.13,Main,God,0,0,0,,{that can top dying and getting \Nresurrected in another world.}... dibangkitkan di dunia lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.77,0:07:31.48,Main,God,0,0,0,,{Looks like your smartphone \Nis working fine, too.}HP-mu pun sepertinya \Nmasih berfungsi dengan baik.
