Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:34.45,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{It's been a big help to me.}Berkat Anda, saya terbantu banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:40.42,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{I still don't really know what \NI want to do in this world,}Meski belum terlalu mengerti \Napa yang ingin kulakukan di dunia ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:44.62,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{but whatever I decide on will \Nprobably require money,}tapi uang sangat diperlukan \Nuntuk melakukan apa pun, jadi
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.62,0:07:48.39,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{so for now, I'll keep working on \Ncompleting extermination quests.}aku berniat terus begini dan \Nmenuntaskan misi pembasmian.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.39,0:07:50.65,Main,God,0,0,0,,{I see, I see.}Begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:54.64,Main,God of Love,0,0,0,,{Why haffn'h you sheh your \Nfianshées as your hhmm shreen?}Kenapa tidak pakai foto \Ntunangan sebagai layar beranda?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:55.39,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:07:57.41,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{If I set my fiancées as my home screen,}Bukannya kalau aku \Npasang di layar beranda ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:08:00.23,Main,Touya,0,0,0,,{it would it be super \Nembarrassing if I ever lost it!}... nanti bakal malu \Nbanget misal pas jatuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:03.69,Main,God,0,0,0,,{I'm surprised you could understand her.}Kamu tahu betul \Ntentang yang barusan, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:06.33,Main,Love,0,0,0,,{What's wrong with that?}Enggak apa, lah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.33,0:08:09.30,Main,Love,0,0,0,,{Laughing and blushing over having \Nyour loved ones as your home screen...}Ketawa-ketiwi dan tersipu saat \Nlihat foto doi di layar beranda.
